      "notes": "initialize() reads JSON via JsonFile + ArrayLoader. write() uses ArrayDumper, writes installed.json, optionally generates installed.php and copies InstalledVersions.php if $dumpVersions=true. safelyLoadInstalledVersions validates and evals installed.php."
